View_Interfaces

Interface ITargetDefinitionTab

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITab, ITextTab, IView, java.util.Observer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TargetDefinitionTab

    public interface ITargetDefinitionTab
extends ITextTab
    This tab interface provides functionality to edit the target definition of a requirement analysis. It is based on ITextTab and shows the ITargetDefinition of the current IRequirementAnalysis in a text field which could be edited. The possible view actions are the same as described in ITextTab.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    9045534
